+/**
+ * Per-field KNN vectors format for the KNN1040 codec. Uses {@link Lucene99HnswVectorsFormat}
+ * for HNSW, {@link Lucene99RWHnswScalarQuantizedVectorsFormat} for scalar quantization (to
