From 2999eba5ad1d60cbf8ad41efbc447ac27dd3821d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vijayan Balasubramanian <balasvij@amazon.com>
Date: Wed, 18 Mar 2026 21:16:04 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 19/53] Introduce NativeEngines990KnnVectorsScorer to decouple
 native SIMD scoring selection from FaissMemoryOptimizedSearcher (#3184)

Move native SIMD scorer selection into FlatVectorsScorer decorator

Extract MMap/native scorer selection from FaissMemoryOptimizedSearcher
into a FlatVectorsScorer decorator, making native SIMD available across
all scoring paths (including HNSW traversal).

Wrap NativeRandomVectorScorer with PrefetchableFlatVectorScorer to enable
prefetch-aware bulk scoring for mmap vectors, reducing memory latency.

Key changes:
- Add NativeEngines990KnnVectorsScorer for transparent native scorer routing
- Simplify FaissMemoryOptimizedSearcher (remove native branching)
- Refactor NativeRandomVectorScorer to extend AbstractRandomVectorScorer
- Wire scorer into codec chain before prefetch layer
- Add tests for all routing paths

Signed-off-by: Vijayan Balasubramanian <balasvij@amazon.com>
